title: (Weds Early Bird) Jelly Roll In-Studio on his friendship with The Rock and What He Learned from Jail + Never Gonna Get It! With Listener Jeff
itunes:title: (Weds Early Bird) Jelly Roll In-Studio on his friendship with The Rock and What He Learned from Jail + Never Gonna Get It! With Listener Jeff
description:
Jelly Roll stops by the studio. Bobby talks to him about his friendship with the Rock, his new country song and what he learned from his time in jail. In the Never Gonna Get It Question: You see it all the time on TV, but three-fifths of Americans say they've never found themselves in this situation. What is it?
